title: Ganbare! Kieruna!! Shikiso Usuko-san
original_name: がんばれ! 消えるな!! 色素薄子さん
sinopse:
People say, there's no one as invisible as Usuko-san. But does that mean she is miserable? Not at all! This a tale of Usuko-san's happy happy life. Read how Usuko survives her days at her new university.

(Source: MangaHelpers)
